{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2488","id":3679458921,"node_id":"PR_kwDOEHbxG87bUBZp","html_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2488","diff_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2488.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2488.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2488","number":2488,"state":"closed","locked":false,"title":"sysdolphin: split hsd_3B34 JPEG routines","user":{"login":"itsgrimetime","id":990274,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk5MDI3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/990274?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime","html_url":"https://github.com/itsgrimetime","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"## Summary\n- split the hsd_3B34 range into hsd_3B34 and hsd_3B5C translation units\n- add nonmatching C for the JPEG encode/decode routines in both TUs\n- keep hsd_803B5C2C matching at 100% and improve the surrounding fuzzy matches\n\n## TU split rationale\nThe split at hsd_803B5C4C looked like a natural TU boundary rather than just an arbitrary function boundary. The original combined range had clean adjacent extab/extabindex cut points there, and the data sections also separated cleanly: hsd_3B34 owns the first static JPEG table cluster through lbl_80430C40 / .sdata2 804DEB90, while hsd_3B5C begins with a separate large table at lbl_80431090 and its own .sdata2 constants.\n\nhsd_803B5C2C also behaved like a small end-of-first-cluster routine and matched 100% immediately before hsd_803B5C4C starts the decode-side helper cluster. That combination made the split a plausible TU boundary, and the rebuilt sections/link check corroborate it.\n\n## Match status\n- hsd_3B34: 84.855255% fuzzy\n- hsd_3B5C: 84.95146% fuzzy\n\n## Verification\n- pre-commit run --files src/sysdolphin/baselib/hsd_3B34.c src/sysdolphin/baselib/hsd_3B34.h src/sysdolphin/baselib/hsd_3B5C.c\n- python configure.py --wrapper build/tools/wibo && ninja","created_at":"2026-05-13T23:03:36Z","updated_at":"2026-05-16T08:45:49Z","closed_at":"2026-05-14T08:42:25Z","merged_at":"2026-05-14T08:42:25Z","merge_commit_sha":"cce285d6481724d3b573a046ac859daf68e98d7d","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2488/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2488/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2488/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/3d5449d60bfd21d89ba410fdd8a6a544d13a68b0","head":{"label":"itsgrimetime:pr/hsd-3b34-3b5c","ref":"pr/hsd-3b34-3b5c","sha":"3d5449d60bfd21d89ba410fdd8a6a544d13a68b0","user":{"login":"itsgrimetime","id":990274,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk5MDI3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/990274?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime","html_url":"https://github.com/itsgrimetime","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/following{/other_user}","gists_url